<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_ævæccægæn" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><form type="lemma"><orth>ævæccægæn</orth><lang/></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>вероятно</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>probably</q></cit></sense><re xml:lang="os-x-digor"><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><lang/><form type="lemma"><orth>ævæʒi</orth><lang/></form></re><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_ævæccægæn." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>ævæccægæn zaǧta: k˳yst — cardæn færæz</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>должно быть, она сказала: труд — средство к жизни</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>Probably, she said: work is a means to life</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>55</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>ævæccægæn zaǧta: k˳yst — cardæn færæz</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>должно быть, она сказала: труд — средство к жизни</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>Probably, she said: work is a means to life</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>55</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Сращение префикса %iav%i- с <xr><ref target="#entry_æcæg"/></xr>(æccæg) ‘правда’; конечное -%iæn%i — флексия дательного падежа. Ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒa"/></xr> ‘ведь’, д. <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒi"/></xr> ‘вероятно’. См. <xr><ref target="#entry_æcæg"/><ref target="#entry_æccæj"/></xr>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">The fusion of the prefix %iav%i- and <xr><ref target="#entry_æcæg"/></xr>(æccæg) ‘truth’; the final -%iæn%i is dative case flection. Compare <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒa"/></xr> ‘after all’, Digor <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒi"/></xr> ‘probably’. See <xr><ref target="#entry_æcæg"/><ref target="#entry_æccæj"/></xr>.</etym></entry>